OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FIn the Budget, Rachel Reeves confirmed
OL,7,Fchanges to how business rates ` the
OL,8,Ftax affecting commercial properties `
OL,9,Fwill be calculated, including a new
OL,10,Fmultiplier from next year.
OL,12,FThe chancellor also announced the
OL,13,Fphasing out of a Covid-era relief
OL,14,Foffered to businesses - a discount of
OL,15,F40% - from April.
