OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FReeves pledged the lowest permanent
OL,7,Fbusiness rates since 1991 for more
OL,8,Fthan 750,000 retail, leisure and
OL,9,Fhospitality businesses, but experts
OL,10,Fargued the changes will result in a
OL,11,Fsharp annual increase in costs.
OL,13,FUKHospitality analysis has found the
OL,14,Faverage pub's business rates will
OL,15,Fincrease 15% next year - an extra
OL,16,F#1,400 - even with the reduced
OL,17,Fmultiplier and when taking into
OL,18,Faccount transitional relief.
