OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FOne west London pub owner told ITV
OL,7,FNews his costs will increase from
OL,8,Faround #2,500 to more than #20,000 per
OL,9,Fyear, while another said he will have
OL,10,Fto pay 92% more in business rates than
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FHowever, there are exemptions for some
OL,14,Fsmall businesses as many receive
OL,15,Fdifferent types of relief.
