OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FSacha Lord, chairman of the Night Time
OL,7,FIndustries Association (NTIA), called
OL,8,Fthe changes "catastrophic for the
OL,9,Feconomy", saying they will force
OL,10,Fbusiness closures, cost people's jobs
OL,11,Fand "crucify" the sector.
OL,13,FWhat was announced in the Budget?
OL,15,FBusiness rates are taxes charged on
OL,16,Fmost non-domestic properties, like
OL,17,Fcouncil taxes paid on homes.
OL,19,FThey're calculated by multiplying the
OL,20,Frateable value of a property by a
OL,21,Fmultiplier.
