OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the chancellor announced
OL,7,Fthat the multiplier would decrease
OL,8,Ffrom 49p in the pound to 43p.
OL,10,FRateable value changes
OL,12,FAfter the initial Budget announcement,
OL,13,Fthe Treasury published new rateable
OL,14,Fvalues for properties, which will
OL,15,Faffect how much property tax
OL,16,Fbusinesses will pay from the next
OL,17,Ffinancial year.
OL,19,FDespite business rates going down, the
OL,20,Frateable value of some properties will
OL,21,Fincrease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
