OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FA third factor affecting business
OL,7,Fcosts is the phasing out of financial
OL,8,Fsupport for businesses introduced
OL,9,Fduring Covid and replaced with smaller
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FThe government confirmed a current 40%
OL,13,Fdiscount for retail, hospitality and
OL,14,Fleisure businesses ` which is capped
OL,15,Fat #110,000 per business ` will end on
OL,16,FMarch 31 next year.
OL,18,FHowever, the government insists a new
OL,19,F#3.2 billion transitional relief
OL,20,Fscheme will provide support for
OL,21,Fbusinesses paying higher rates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
