OL,6,FReeves argued the reforms would make
OL,7,Fthe system fairer and said the old
OL,8,Frules, including "cliff-edges" in
OL,9,Freliefs - where businesses lose
OL,10,Fsupport when expanding - were a
OL,11,Fdisincentive to growth.
OL,13,FBut analysis from tax firm Ryan
OL,14,Findicated the change and an increase
OL,15,Fin rateable values for most pubs will
OL,16,Fresult in a sharp annual increase.
OL,18,FIt found the average pub will see a
OL,19,Fbill of #9,264.93 this financial year
OL,20,Frise by 65.9% to #15,373.59 for 2026/
OL,21,F27.
