OL,6,FThe analysis also indicated that
OL,7,Frestaurants will see their rates bills
OL,8,Fjump by 44.9% from April, while small
OL,9,Fshops will see a rise of around 42.3%.
OL,11,F'It was a shock'
OL,13,FPeter Brew, landlord of The Black Dog
OL,14,FBeer House, told ITV News it "was an
OL,15,Fabsolute shock" when he calculated the
OL,16,Fnew rateable value for his pub on the
OL,17,Fgovernment website.
OL,19,FHe said he is facing an increase of
OL,20,Faround #20,000 per year, which he
OL,21,Fcalled "crazy".
