OL,6,FKate Nicholls, Chair of UKHospitality,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The government promised in its
OL,8,Fmanifesto that it would level the
OL,9,Fplaying field between the high street
OL,10,Fand online giants. The plan in the
OL,11,FBudget to achieve this is quickly
OL,12,Funravelling, and will deliver the
OL,13,Fexact opposite.
OL,15,F"Our analysis shows that hospitality
OL,16,Fbusinesses will be paying more. Pubs
OL,17,Fwill see bills increase by thousands
OL,18,Fand hotels by tens of thousands.
