OL,6,F"We repeatedly warned the Treasury
OL,7,Fahead of the Budget that hospitality
OL,8,Fwould be uniquely impacted by
OL,9,Fsignificant increases to rateable
OL,10,Fvalues, due to the pandemic impacting
OL,11,Fprevious valuations. This had to be
OL,12,Ffactored into the level of business
OL,13,Frates discount it offered the sector.
OL,15,F"The eye-watering increases pubs,
OL,16,Fhotels and other venues are now waking
OL,17,Fup to was exactly the reason why the
OL,18,FTreasury had to implement the maximum
OL,19,Fpossible discount. The decision not to
OL,20,Fdo so will lead to higher bills next
OL,21,Fyear.
